com.aspose.cells
Class Title

java.lang.Object
  ChartFrame
      ChartTextFrame
          com.aspose.cells.Title

public class Title 
extends ChartTextFrame

Encapsulates the object that represents the title of chart or axis.

Example:

//Setting the title of a chart
chart.getTitle().setText("Title");
//Setting the font color of the chart title to blue
chart.getTitle().getTextFont().setColor(Color.getBlue());
//Setting the title of category axis of the chart
chart.getCategoryAxis().getTitle().setText("Category");
//Setting the title of value axis of the chart
chart.getValueAxis().getTitle().setText("Value");
